ies and equipment to complement your unique playstyle. Strategically combine a vast array of skill cards and gear to create a powerful and versatile team.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157800/extras/3febb60bcef8c368b06c9a1947432de1.poster.avif?t=1725339917\" width=600 height=263 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157800/extras/3febb60bcef8c368b06c9a1947432de1.webm?t=1725339917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Unravel a compelling narrative that challenges the very concept of value. Discover how the power of money can be harnessed to save the world in this epic tale of heroism and economic might.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157800/extras/5bbd32e405695aeabd4cfcd3f387c6a6.poster.avif?t=1725339917\" width=600 height=263 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157800/extras/5bbd32e405695aeabd4cfcd3f387c6a6.webm?t=1725339917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Prepare to immerse yourself in a world where every decision matters. Will you lead your party to victory or succumb to the darkness? The fate of Grand Terra rests in your hands.",
